{"tid":2035470,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"個仔離開左，個心好痛，有無人可以一齊安慰下","createTime":"2020-05-26T02:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T05:40:15.000Z","uid":174245,"like":43,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8dbf9e01301b93c06bf1a2e7c8e65ccb8ce14d4b","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"尋日8點幾離開，個心痛到唔知有咩好寫，個思緒好亂，整理唔到咁。有無人可以話我知你地係點樣抽離同釋懷，一feel到間屋咁靜，望住佢以前咬開既骨骨，我就好掛住好掛住佢以前好可愛既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全訓唔著，果種瞇埋眼但個腦係空既，好似唔識訓覺既感覺好辛苦。念起佢又掛住佢，好心好似就黎裂開咁。我真係好愛好愛好愛好愛佢，雖然知道佢唔會翻黎，但個感覺真係好難受"},{"pid":"eafa0f252dc8ffd68df0d0545d059b018bf776cf","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"由佢病到尋日，都係1個禮拜，點解黎得咁突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ea1e2702a19e64d1659fc9c46159ec24fa9534","tid":2035470,"uid":106633,"like":15,"dislike":29,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"人定狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956e4c9a672e6174ddfdfb7daf2f5391893b4d20","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":9,"dislike":33,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"55ea1e2702a19e64d1659fc9c46159ec24fa9534","tid":2035470,"uid":106633,"like":15,"dislike":29,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"人定狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"寵物台..."},{"pid":"28d3d558eb208758ac2be6609e67176b61328b28","tid":2035470,"uid":30604,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"幾歲呀？我明<br />\n我有隻都係十幾歲走左，所以我以後唔敢再養....<br />\n因為真係好撚傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"20ad43779fdb84bae9992a26508f50bd