,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"咩病禁快走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"一開始啲腎指數好高，以為可能係腎有事，跟住尋另一個醫生check，見到個胃壁有異樣，比平時既胃壁增厚左1cm，懷疑係惡can<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住尋日就走左... 不過佢應該真係好痛好痛...平時最鍾意吃嘢，超級為食，竟然成10日無吃過嘢...好心痛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d367b06ed8af4e23a26a2f11b546fdbe31357f39","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b8bd2444936998d6da2d166c641fcc28ad38606","tid":2035470,"uid":30604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"50d58cf64f0e5720ef571dd14a55779c57699025","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"023aca1175c7182a918a2f3a9abb49a496d3d6d3","tid":2035470,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"我果隻2015走 我係鐘意狗 但係到今日我真係無衝動再養<br />\n因為真係好撚辛苦 果陣我真係喊撚左成個禮拜<br />\n而家都係撚下人地隻狗 唔敢養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"5年都未釋懷？好驚自己過幾年都釋懷唔到，好驚一唸起佢就喊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:06:29.000Z","msg":"邊有得釋懷 今時今日 wallpaper都仲用緊佢張相<br />\n你只可以諗你已經好錫佢對佢好好 陪佢走過左十一年<br />\n已經無悔啦 let it go..<br />\n只係純粹有陰影唔敢再養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"唉...好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ee2d452948bc6b83cbfe5c2287f9034332373f","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63ed28fc805023358bafae48f225697a97df7ac4","tid":2035470,"uid":44562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"囝囝走咗唔使受苦都係一件好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"一開始仲唸過幫佢打針走...等佢唔洗咁痛...見完最後一眼..比我地抱左下，佢自己就走左去自己張床訓低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7b17b7d63ebf70c27ac7a19de0e62ae44583be","tid":2035470,"uid":119341,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8dbf9e01301b93c06bf1a2e7c8e65ccb8ce14d4b","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"尋日8點幾離開，個心痛到唔知有咩好寫，個思緒好亂，整理唔到咁。有無人可以話我知你地係點樣抽離同釋懷，一feel到間屋咁靜，望住佢以前咬開既骨骨，我就好掛住好掛住佢以前好可愛既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全訓唔著，果種瞇埋眼但個腦係空既，好似唔識訓覺既感覺好辛苦。念起佢又掛住佢，好心好似就黎裂開咁。我真係好愛好愛好愛好愛佢，雖然知道佢唔會翻黎，但個感覺真係好難受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"我狗狗離開後系有返黎過，明顯聽到動靜，而且有聲經常傳出，大概持續一兩個星期。我當時日日自己念經文超度，之後幾日夢見狗狗返黎同我講，之後會再見面。從發完個夢之後就開始釋懷。"},{"pid":"4459e51961b1bc01713d7564fcd7605e21b7d510","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"屋企貓貓今日都照到有腎衰竭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好突然好驚佢會走<br />\n但話都捱唔到幾耐<br />\n唉樓主共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a4735e80fc62f9fdb87182405cf9011824086c","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4459e51961b1bc01713d7564fcd7605e21b7d510","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"屋企貓貓今日都照到有腎衰竭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好突然好驚佢會走<br />\n但話都捱唔到幾耐<br />\n唉樓主共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醫生有無話幾多期？你個bb幾多歲啊"},{"pid":"080303a301ed2bc12e03623df3cd544b926546b2","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4459e51961b1bc01713d7564fcd7605e21b7d510","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"屋企貓貓今日都照到有腎衰竭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好突然好驚佢會走<br />\n但話都捱唔到幾耐<br />\n唉樓主共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"記得同佢做多啲佢鍾意既嘢，嘢多幾張相，佢一定會開心，佢都會知道佢好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031a90bb36666d31d6c1a95cad746f845235450c","tid":2035470,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"唔會釋懷。我囡囡3年前走咗，心痛好耐。差不多 15歲。<br />\n<br />\n今世唔會再養。<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 樓主節衰順變。死亡亦是生命一部分，自然定律"},{"pid":"d870f7eeb4f682e079e067f0496a028b0ce401ea","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080303a301ed2bc12e03623df3cd544b926546b2","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4459e51961b1bc01713d7564fcd7605e21b7d510","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"屋企貓貓今日都照到有腎衰竭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好突然好驚佢會走<br />\n但話都捱唔到幾耐<br />\n唉樓主共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"記得同佢做多啲佢鍾意既嘢，嘢多幾張相，佢一定會開心，佢都會知道佢好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"睇到依句就忍唔住喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10歲啦都<br />\n話做手術會好轉但亦有機會有併發症<br />\n唔忍心依個年紀重要佢捱依刀所以重考慮緊<br />\n定同佢開開心心玩好過"},{"pid":"6820b6298b47b29dddb2cbf643b47cbf655a806e","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d870f7eeb4f682e079e067f0496a028b0ce401ea","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080303a301ed2bc12e03623df3cd544b926546b2","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4459e51961b1bc01713d7564fcd7605e21b7d510","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"屋企貓貓今日都照到有腎衰竭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好突然好驚佢會走<br />\n但話都捱唔到幾耐<br />\n唉樓主共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"記得同佢做多啲佢鍾意既嘢，嘢多幾張相，佢一定會開心，佢都會知道佢好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"睇到依句就忍唔住喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10歲啦都<br />\n話做手術會好轉但亦有機會有併發症<br />\n唔忍心依個年紀重要佢捱依刀所以重考慮緊<br />\n定同佢開開心心玩好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"開刀有時真係好危險，好多貓狗都係捱左刀過一排就離開。不過可能唔係隻隻都會咁，只不過如果咁大年紀，我都唔會想比佢又麻醉又捱一刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過希望你貓貓無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩事記得唔好屈住 可以係到講，分擔下痛苦，或者都係一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e76e2674ffd5f36aa5c3f14e8aa8d258ffeb75","tid":2035470,"uid":296604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"我早兩年養左14年既貓貓都走左<br />\n近排因為有朋友既貓生左bb俾左兩隻我地<br />\n頭一個禮拜望到佢地諗起以前隻貓都會係咁喊<br />\n尤其佢地搵返以前隻貓整唔見左既玩具出黎個下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好難釋懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550ef39018baaacdafcc4fec0b71af03f220141e","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82e76e2674ffd5f36aa5c3f14e8aa8d258ffeb75","tid":2035470,"uid":296604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"我早兩年養左14年既貓貓都走左<br />\n近排因為有朋友既貓生左bb俾左兩隻我地<br />\n頭一個禮拜望到佢地諗起以前隻貓都會係咁喊<br />\n尤其佢地搵返以前隻貓整唔見左既玩具出黎個下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好難釋懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"仲以為有新既貓貓會可以分散下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過佢地一定會知道我地好愛佢地，佢地都會好似我地咁愛翻我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee501cdad8845c5c3929ecafef8400e01df4ab8","tid":2035470,"uid":69231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:56:35.000Z","msg":"當初養佢預左有咁既一日<br />\n唯有靠時間慢慢走出傷痛<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢都唔想你一直唔開心<br />\n而且你地既回憶係會一直保存落去<br />\n希望你隻寵物可以去到一個<br />\n無憂無慮既地方生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b7f1c48cbdbe6f4abc44366d54a62011a18642","tid":2035470,"uid":301551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢世都唔會釋懷<br />\n我屋企三仔爺貓貓養到十幾歲<br />\n走哂了<br />\n今年仲前後走左兩隻<br />\n好想再養但應該唔會養了"},{"pid":"3170c27e9ad14a763850e1cf3cb545ff5a6a31fd","tid":2035470,"uid":301551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d870f7eeb4f682e079e067f0496a028b0ce401ea","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080303a301ed2bc12e03623df3cd544b926546b2","tid":2035470,"uid":174245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4459e51961b1bc01713d7564fcd7605e21b7d510","tid":2035470,"uid":11134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"屋企貓貓今日都照到有腎衰竭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好突然好驚佢會走<br />\n但話都捱唔到幾耐<br />\n唉樓主共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:16:58.000Z","msg":"記得同佢做多啲佢鍾意既嘢，嘢多幾張相，佢一定會開心，佢都會知道佢好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"睇到依句就忍唔住喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10歲啦都<br />\n話做手術會好轉但亦有機會有併發症<br />\n唔忍心依個年紀重要佢捱依刀所以重考慮緊<br />\n定同佢開開心心玩好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"腎衰竭有得開刀醫架咩<br />\n因為我養過三隻其中一隻係腎衰走的"},{"pid":"7a551389d85a09